    "Such spillover effects can help less AI-literate executives develop or improve an AI understanding, resulting in more realistic expectations about the possibilities of AI technologies like machine learning.",
    "By promoting a thorough understanding of AI and communicating its potential impact, AI-literate executives can motivate other executives to support AI orientation (Li et al., 2021).",
